         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits. To Claudia Aphro. She lived for twenty-two years (and)
                    five months. Lathymus, (the slave) of Medon, (the slave) of Cocceus Nerva, made
                    (this) for (his) wife, well-deserving. </p>
